\c 34
\s Josiya mambo waJudha anogadzira temberi nokudzosa vanhu kuna Jehovha
\p
\v 1 Josiya akatanga kubata ushe ava namakore masere; akabata ushe paJerusarema makore makumi matatu nerimwe.
\v 2 Akaita zvakarurama pamberi paJehovha, akafamba nenzira yababa vake Dhavhidhi, haana kutsaukira kurudyi kana kuruboshwe.
\p
\v 3 nekuti pagore rorusere rokubata kwake ushe, achiri muduku, akatanga kutsvaka Mwari waDhavhidhi baba vake; zvino pagore regumi namaviri akatanga kunatsa Judha neJerusarema, achibvisa matunhu akakwirira, namatanda okunamata nawo nemifananidzo yakavezwa, nemifananidzo yakaumbwa.
\v 4 Vakakoromora aritari dzavaBhaari, iye aripo; akatema aritari dzezvipfungaidzo zvinonhuwira dzakange dzakaitwa pamusoro padzo; akaputsanya matanda okunamata nawo, nemifananidzo yakavezwa, nemifananidzo yakaumbwa, akazvikuya zvikaita guruva, akarisasa pamarinda avaizvibayira.
\v 5 Akapisa mafupa avapristi paaritari dzavo, akanatsa Judha neJerusarema.
\v 6 Akaitawo saizvozvo pamaguta aManase naEfuremu naSimioni, kusvikira paNafutari, pamatongo awo.
\p
\v 7 Akaputsa aritari, akakuya matanda okunamata nawo nemifananidzo yakavezwa zvikaita guruva, akatema mifananidzo yose yezuva panyika yose yaIsraeri, ndokudzokera Jerusarema.
\p
\v 8 Zvino pagore regumi namasere rokubata kwake ushe, akati anatsa nyika neimba, ndokutuma Shafani mwanakomana waAzaria, naMaaseya, mubati weguta, naJoa mwanakomana waJohazi, gurukota, kundogadzira imba yaJehovha Mwari wake.
\v 9 Vakasvika kuna Hirikia mupristi mukuru, vakamupa mari yakange yaiswa mumba yaMwari, yakange yaunganidzwa navaRevhi, vatariri vemikova, pakati paManase paEfuremu, navose vakasara vavaIsraeri navaJudha vose, navaBhenjamini, navakange vagere Jerusarema.
\v 10 Vakaipa pamaoko avabati vakange vachitarira imba yaJehovha, vakairipa kuzovandudza nokugadzirisa imba;
\v 11 vakaipa vavezi navavaki, kuti vatenge mabwe akavezwa namatanda okubatanidza, nokuita mapango edzimba dzakange dzaparadzwa namadzimambo aJudha.
\v 12 Vanhu avo vakabata basa nokutendeka; vatariri vavo vaiva Jahati naObhadhiya, vaRevhi vavanakomana vaMerari, naZekariya, naMeshurami, vavanakomana vaKohati, kuzoraira basa; navamwe vaRevhi, vose vaiziva kuridza zvinoridzwa.
\v 13 Ivo vaitarirawo vatakuri vemitoro, vakarairawo vose vaibata mabasa amarudzi ose; pakati pavaRevhi pakange panavanyori, navatariri, navarindi vemikova.
\p
\v 14 Zvino vakati vachibudisa mari yakange yaiswa mumba maJehovha, mupristi Hirikia ndokuwana bhuku yomurayiro waJehovha, wakange wapiwa naMozisi.
\v 15 Hirikia akapindura, akati kuna Shafani munyori, Ndawana bhuku yomurayiro mumba maJehovha. Hirikia ndokupa bhuku iyo kuna Shafani.
\v 16 Zvino Shafani akaenda nebhuku kuna mambo, uye akendawo neshoko kuna mambo, akati, Zvose zvakarairwa varanda venyu, vanozviita.
\p
\v 17 Vakadurura mari yakawanikwa mumba maJehovha, vakaiisa mumaoko avatariri, nomumaoko avabati vebasa.
\v 18 Zvino Shafani munyori akaudza mambo, akati, mupristi Hirikia andipa bhuku. Ipapo Shafani akaravamo pamberi pamambo.
\v 19 Zvino mambo akati achinzwa mashoko omurayiro, akabvarura nguwo dzake.
\v 20 Mambo .akaraira Hirikia naAhikami mwanakomana waShafani, naAbhidhoni mwanakomana waMika, naShafani munyori, naAsaya muranda wamambo, akati,
\v 21 Endai mundondibvunzira Jehovha, ini navakasara vaIsraeri navaJudha pamusoro pamashoko ebhuku yakawanikwa; nekuti kutsamwa kwaJehovha, kwadururwa pamusoro pedu, kukuru, nekuti madzibaba edu haana kuchengeta shoko raJehovha, kuti vaite zvose zvakanyorwa mubhuku iyi.
\p
\v 22 Ipapo Hirikia navakange varairwa namambo vakaenda kuna Huridha muporofitakadzi, mukadzi waSharumi mwanakomana waTokihati, mwanakomana waHazira, muchengeti wenguvo (zvino iye akange agere Jerusarema kuRupandi Rwepiri rweguta;) vakataura naye saizvozvo.
\v 23 Iye akati kwavari, Zvanzi naJehovha Mwari waIsraeri, Udzai munhu akakutumai kwandiri, muti,
\v 24 Zvanzi naJehovha, tarirai, ndichauyisa zvakaipa pamusoro penzvimbo iyi, napamusoro pavagerepo, iko kutuka kose kwakanyorwa mubhuku iyo yavakarava pamberi pamambo waJudha.
\v 25 nekuti vakandirasha, vakapisira vamwe vamwari zvinonhuhwira, vakanditsamwisa namabasa ose amaoko avo; naizvozvo kutsamwa kwangu kwadururwa pamusoro penzvimbo iyi, hakungadzimwi.
\p
\v 26 Asi muti kuna mambo waJudha, akakutumai kuzobvunza Jehovha, Zvanzi naJehovha Mwari waIsraeri, kana ari mashoko awakanzwa,
\v 27 moyo wako zvawakange uri munyoro, ukazvininipisa pamberi paMwari, nguva yawakanzwa mashoko ake pamusoro penzvimbo iyi, napamusoro pavageremo, ukazvininipisa pamberi pangu, ukabvarura nguwo dzako, ukachema pamberi pangu, zvino zvanzi naJehovha, Ini ndakunzwawo.
\p
\v 28 Tarira, ndichakuisa kumadzibaba ako, uchavigwa muhwiro nomufaro; meso ako haangaoni zvakaipa zvose zvandichauyisa pamusoro penzvimbo iyi, navanhu vageremo. Vakadzoka neshoko kuna mambo.
\p
\v 29 Ipapo mambo akatuma vanhu vakaunganidza vakuru vose vaJudha naveJerusarema.
\v 30 Mambo akakwira kumba kwaJehovha, ana varume vose vaJudha, navose vakange vagere Jerusarema, navapristi, navaRevhi, navanhu vose, vakuru navaduku; akavaravira mashoko ose ebhuku yesungano yakange yawanikwa mumba maJehovha.
\v 31 Mambo akamira panzvimbo yake, akaita sungano pamberi paJehovha, akazvisunga kutevera Jehovha, nokuchengeta mirairo yake, nezvipupuriro zvake, nezvaakatema, nomoyo wake wose nomweya wake wose, kuti aite mashoko esungano akanyorwa mubhuku iyi.
\v 32 Akaraira vose vakange vari Jerusarema naBhenjamini kuabvumira. Vagere Jerusarema vakaita sezvakarehwa pasungano yaMwari, iye Mwari wamadzibaba avo.
\v 33 Josiya akabvisa zvakange zvichinyangadza zvose panyika dzose dzaiva dzavaIsraeri, akaraira vose vakange vari pakati paIsraeri kushumira Mwari, kushumira iye Jehovha Mwari wavo. Mazuva ake ose havana kutsauka pakutevera Jehovha Mwari wamadzibaba avo.
